graph TB
    START([Start]) --> IDENTIFY[Identify data element<br/>in use case analysis]
    
    IDENTIFY --> CHECK{Check existing<br/>PH Core profiles}
    
    CHECK -->|Profile exists| USE[Use existing<br/>PH Core profile]
    CHECK -->|No profile| COUNT{Used by ≥2<br/>independent IGs?}
    
    COUNT -->|Yes| CANDIDATE[Mark as PH Core<br/>candidate]
    COUNT -->|No| EXCEPTION{Exception criteria?<br/>Policy priority / Critical / Safety}
    
    EXCEPTION -->|Yes| APPRAISAL[Human appraisal<br/>by PH Core team]
    EXCEPTION -->|No| PROGRAM[Keep as<br/>program-specific]
    
    APPRAISAL -->|Approved| CANDIDATE
    APPRAISAL -->|Denied| PROGRAM
    
    CANDIDATE --> PROFILE[Create PH Core profile<br/>following conventions]
    PROFILE --> DOCUMENT[Document in<br/>Decision Log]
    DOCUMENT --> PUBLISH[Publish in<br/>PH Core IG]
    
    USE --> END([End])
    PROGRAM --> END
    PUBLISH --> END
    
    style START fill:#bbdefb
    style END fill:#bbdefb
    style CANDIDATE fill:#c8e6c9
    style PROGRAM fill:#ffcc80
    style COUNT fill:#fff9c4
    style EXCEPTION fill:#fff9c4
